Hygienic, healthy and economical Lacquered Door models can be used with peace of mind in all interior spaces with various pattern and model alternatives.

MDF is a high-quality durable material that can be processed with CNC machines and on which unique patterns can be created by engraving. Thanks to modern technology, the possibilities for door design are almost unlimited.

Lacquered MDF doors, which are coated with a special varnish, have a bright appearance and a long service life under normal use and maintenance.

All our models of Lacquered MDF doors are a cost-effective solution and are manufactured by using modern equipment, have high quality and a long warranty.
